		{"id":"0b46fc81b452960b","type":"text","text":"# 平面第一型曲线积分\n积分变量是 $ds$.\n\n曲线 $L$ 的周长:\n$$\nC=\\int_{L}ds\n$$\n如果曲线是直角坐标表达的\n$$\n\\int_{L}f(x,y)ds=\\int^{b}_{a}f(x,y(x))\\sqrt{ 1+(y'_{x})^2 }dx\n$$\n\n如果是参数方程表达的\n$$\n\\int_{L}f(y(t),x(t))\\sqrt{ (x'(t))^2+(y'(t))^2 }dt\n$$\n如果是极坐标表达的\n$$\n\\int_{L}f(\\theta, r(\\theta)) \\sqrt{ r^2(\\theta) + (r'(\\theta))^2 } d \\theta\n$$\n\n>[!note] \n>在第一型曲线积分中, 由于在曲线上积分, 因此可以:\n>1. **将曲线的方程代入被积函数**\n>2. 使用轮换对称性, 奇偶对称性\n\n# 空间第一型曲线积分\n空间第一型曲线积分没有公式计算, 在真题中考察的都是使用轮换和奇偶对称性进行计算.\n\n## 18 数一\n\n![[Pasted image 20241204130415.png]]\n\n可知\n$$\n\\oint_{L}x^2+y^2+z^2 ds = 2\\pi, \\oint_{L}x+y+z=0,\\oint_{L}xy=\\oint_{L}yz=\\oint_{L}xz\n$$\n故\n$$\n\\oint_{L}xy = \\dfrac{1}{6} \\oint_{L}(x+y+z)^2-(x^2+y^2+z^2) = -\\dfrac{\\pi}{3}\n$$","x":820,"y":-316,"width":1020,"height":1196},
		{"id":"a7651391d6bc85ff","type":"text","text":"![[Pasted image 20241204125626.png]]\n\n$$\n\\int_{L}x^2+y^2ds = \\int_{L}ds = \\pi \n$$\n![[Pasted image 20241204125743.png]]\n\n由奇偶对称性\n$$\n\\oint_{L}2xy = 0\n$$\n$$\n\\dfrac{x^2}{4}+\\dfrac{y^2}{3} =1 \\implies 3x^2+4y^2 = 12  \\implies \\oint_{L}3x^2+4y^2ds = 12a \n$$\n![[Pasted image 20241204125930.png]]\n$$\n\\int_{L}xds = \\int^{\\sqrt{ 2 }}_{0} x\\sqrt{ 1+4x^2 }dx = \\dfrac{13}{6}\n$$","x":1960,"y":-116,"width":1000,"height":796},
